Understanding Event Binding

v-on:_________specific event could be specified
---------------------------------------------------------------
            <section id="events">
                <h2>Events in Action</h2>
                <button v-on:click="counter++">Add</button>
                <button v-on:click="counter--">Remove</button>
                <p>Result: {{counter}}</p>
            </section>
---------------------------------------------------------------
method could be declared for a specific even

